---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<main class="bg-[#f4e9dc] text-[#222] font-mono px-6 pt-0 pb-12 min-h-screen relative">
  <a href="/" class="absolute left-6 top-6 text-[#542437] bg-[#f4e9dc] border border-[#542437] rounded px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow hover:bg-[#e0c9a6] transition z-10">Home</a>
  <a href="/music" class="absolute left-25 top-6 text-[#542437] bg-[#f4e9dc] border border-[#542437] rounded px-4 py-2 font-semibold shadow hover:bg-[#e0c9a6] transition z-10">Back</a>
  <div class="flex justify-center mb-[-2rem] mt-0">
    <img src="/images/burialpath-logo.png" alt="Burial Path Logo" class="h-[18rem] md:h-[28rem] object-contain pointer-events-none select-none" />
  </div>
  <p class="text-center text-[#444] mb-4 italic">Symphonic Deathcore - "Bury the old. Embrace the rebirth."</p>

  <!-- Streaming Links -->
  <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-6 mb-12 flex-wrap">
    <a href="https://open.spotify.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10">
      <img src="/images/spotify-logo.png" alt="Spotify" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain hover:opacity-80 transition">
    </a>
    <a href="https://music.apple.com/us/artist/burial-path/1743321359" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10">
      <img src="/images/apple-music-logo.png" alt="Apple Music" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain hover:opacity-80 transition">
    </a>
    <a href="https://open.spotify.com/artist/0H3OT5fRfWx8jFkLAEQOIb" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10">
      <img src="/images/bandcamp-logo.png" alt="Bandcamp" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain hover:opacity-80 transition">
    </a>
    <a href="https://music.youtube.com/channel/UCTqsqlSRDZR0diG1GvdKw3g" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center justify-center h-10 w-10">
      <img src="/images/youtube-music-logo.png" alt="YouTube Music" class="h-10 w-10 object-contain hover:opacity-80 transition">
    </a>
  </div>

  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col gap-12">
    <!-- Featured Album Card -->
    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e0c9a6] shadow rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
      <img src="/images/burialpath-album.jpg" alt="Album Cover" class="w-full h-64 object-cover">
      <div class="p-6">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#542437] mb-2">EP 1</h2>
        <p class="text-[#444] mb-2">Releasing Late 2025/Early 2026</p>
        <p class="text-[#666] text-sm">No spoilers! Expect some trailing singles in the months beforehand.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Update/Blog Entry -->

    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e0c9a6] shadow rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#542437] mb-1">Jun-July, 2025 - Finishing singles and EP before sending to mix</h3>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-sm">We're coordinating on trying to get some singles out the door.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e0c9a6] shadow rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#542437] mb-1">May 25, 2025 - Band Photoshoot</h3>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-sm">We just wrapped finished getting updated band photos in Turner Falls, OK.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e0c9a6] shadow rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#542437] mb-1">Mar, 2025 - Tracking Lead Guitar Bits</h3>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-sm">Got my first chances to contribute some tasty lead guitar work and some solos on the upcoming songs. As Aicha calls them: the "weedly deedlies".</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white border border-[#e0c9a6] shadow rounded-xl p-6">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#542437] mb-1">Jan, 2025 - Joining</h3>
      <p class="text-[#666] text-sm">After a successful audition and vibecheck, I joined Burial Path as the lead guitarist. At this point, 3 singles had been released and EP writing was under way.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>